Next  Offline Basic to  pro Chandan class will start from 18th August.
Location -Serampore .
Contact -7003981788

 📣 CHANDAN CLASS DETAILS 📣

🟥1ST DAY

🔵 Brush knowledge and how to use a brush for a long time.
🔵Bindi knowledge (Real or Duplicate).
🔵Fabric mixing knowledge in proper way.
🔵I will show special tricks  for how to make the cheek Kolka equal on both sides.
🔵You will come to know  how much water and fabric need  to mix for forehead Kolka.
🔵There will be some special tricks for how to get thin Kolka in one day.
🔵For those of you whose hands shake while applying Kolka on your bride's forehead, I have a trick for you.
🔵 Knowledge on how to hold your chandan brush on forehead and paper.
🔵How to draw a Kolka motif with a single stroke.
🔵There are many techniques of how to create Kolka by yourself.
🟢 Basic strokes, patterns and leaf motif in very easiest way.
🟢6 types of reception kolka with basic strokes.
🟠1 Reception Kolka demonstration.
🟢 Knowledge of hand kolka.

🟥 2ND DAY

🟢 Advance strokes.
🟢 There will be many floral motifs.
🟢1 Advance reception kolka.
🟢1 Advance bridal Kolka.
🟠1 Floral bridal Kolka demonstration.
🟢 Knowledge of betel leaf kolka.

🟥3RD DAY 

🟢 Elephant, Peacock, Peacock feather, Butterfly,Bird, Trishul motif.
🟠1 sabeki Kolka demonstration.
🟢1 calligraphy kolka.
🟢Red Application.
🟢How to paint clay plate,bowl,glass,gach- kouto painting ideas.

🟥4TH DAY 

🟠Cheek Kolka demonstration.
🟢 Minakari Kolka in my signature way.
🟢 Knowledge of necklace Kolka.
🟢kulo painting ideas.

🟥5TH DAY 

🟠 Potrait Kolka demonstration (shoot Kolka).
🟢Lots of new techniques.

🟥6TH DAY 

🤷 EXAM.

HURRY, ENROLL YOUR NAMES 🖊️🖊️🖊️
